Title: Makes an appropriation to the East End Supervisors and Mayors Association for a feasibility study update relating to the creation of Peconic county
Summary: Makes an appropriation of $200,000 to the East End Supervisors and Mayors Association for a feasibility study update relating to the creation of Peconic county.
ActClause: AN ACT making an appropriation to the East End Supervisors and Mayors Association for a feasibility study update relating to the creation of Peconic county
